係南記越開越多已經比以前差左少少喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望唔好開再多分店"},{"pid":"f3434fe7dfb2df9378f73f7d22c21ae41d8b08cc","tid":101770,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:22:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9b80cbb6efba470e94359bd040d496fab8b707e","tid":101770,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>10年前南記真係好好食<br />\n香港仔巴士站果間最正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger<br />\n<br />\n香港仔以外根本冇間好食<br />\n舊年食過銅記分店，餸冇味，湯底又冇味，難食過屎<br />\n唯一keep到嘅係個辣醬囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger<br />\n<br />\n香港仔撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申前香港仔撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fbbfa9c55358731aa26d19793f3696d25dab2b","tid":101770,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:30:38.000Z","msg":"南哥 好撚難食啵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ebe7f5617e62ce2f87db94132e346b805bb329","tid":101770,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:33:08.000Z","msg":"0負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d8190e731dc344acc253391fdcd625ae85e665","tid":101770,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:38:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果南記開係新界我實日日幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6afec0720ff72350a0aea01be49f6bfa1099ac","tid":101770,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南記好食過譚仔十倍</blockquote><br />\n但係譚仔係0.01<br />\n南記係0.1"},{"pid":"8c94ece9791f1cd749e473ee8362775a136f4dae","tid":101770,"uid":78001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見連登仔成日吹奏 食過一次<br />\n屌你老母真係比狗都唔撚食<br />\n米線又淋 河粉冇特別 <br />\n個湯好似坑渠水咁既色<br />\n特別係咬落去好似食緊屎咁既春卷<br />\n又淋又臭 食左兩啖掉撚左<br />\n咁都要收50蚊 我叫關平黎煮撚下狗仲過癮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果然連登仔食開狗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不能同意更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af1e2b232a09020c07cf47f7b3caa4dc46722f2","tid":101770,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:43:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>南記好食過譚仔十倍</blockquote><br />\n但係譚仔係0.01<br />\n南記係0.1</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未至於既就<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚仔係0.06<br />\n南記係0.6"},{"pid":"dc72d6f41dc3c93dab5883b31455de13f43123e1","tid":101770,"uid":31837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>10年前南記真係好好食<br />\n香港仔巴士站果間最正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger<br />\n<br />\n香港仔以外根本冇間好食<br />\n舊年食過銅記分店，餸冇味，湯底又冇味，難食過屎<br />\n唯一keep到嘅係個辣醬囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger<br />\n<br />\n香港仔撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申前香港仔撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實鍾意謝記多過南記"},{"pid":"e9c089243a94146f341dd8af273ce522ed29ff35","tid":101770,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"南記酸辣米線好撚貴喎<br />\n腩肉米線$38，普通一餸好似都$35，而且份量堅少，普通女仔都係岩岩好<br />\n譚仔價錢平民好多<br />\n而個春卷真係唔明有咩好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d7143752a5ce9bdd9c70637ba763a56d4aaae6","tid":101770,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"下午茶幾抵食"}]}